                            oc:tableCaption "## What Goes Where" ;
                            oc:tableMarkdown """| Type | CLAUDE.md (Hot Cache) | memory/ (Full Storage) |
|------|----------------------|------------------------|
| Person | Top ~30 frequent contacts | glossary.md + people/{name}.md |
